《'''愛'''》（'''''Love'''''）是一部美國的喜劇電視影集。由[[賈德·阿帕托|賈德·阿帕托]]、[[保羅·魯斯特|保羅·魯斯特]]和萊絲莉·亞芬創造，[[吉莉安·賈布斯|吉莉安·賈布斯]]和魯斯特主演。[[Netflix|Netflix]]已預訂本劇兩季集數，第一季10集於2016年2月19日釋出，<ref>{{Cite web|last = Malone|first = Michael|date = 4 January 2015|url = http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/programming/apatow-comedy-love-gets-feb-19-netflix-debut/146656/|title = Apatow Comedy ‘Love’ Gets Feb. 19 Netflix Debut|publisher = ''broadcastingcable.com''|accessdate = 4 January 2015|archive-date = 2016-03-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160302072835/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/programming/apatow-comedy-love-gets-feb-19-netflix-debut/146656/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last1 = Petski|first1 = Denise|url = http://deadline.com/2016/01/judd-apatow-love-netflix-premiere-teaser-1201675508/|title = Judd Apatow Netflix Comedy Series ‘Love’ Gets Premiere Date — First-Look Teaser|work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date = January 4, 2016|accessdate = January 4, 2016|archive-date = 2016-03-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041203/http://deadline.com/2016/01/judd-apatow-love-netflix-premiere-teaser-1201675508/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 第二季12集則預計在隔年推出。<ref name="s2">{{Cite web|last = Littleton|first = Cynthia|date = 16 September 2014|url = http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/netflix-recuits-judd-apatow-handing-2-season-order-lesley-arfin-comedy-love-1201306514/|title = Netflix Recruits Judd Apatow, Handing 2-Season Order to Lesley Arfin Comedy 'Love'|publisher = ''Variety.com''|access-date = 2016-02-20|archive-date = 2014-09-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140919094111/http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/netflix-recuits-judd-apatow-handing-2-season-order-lesley-arfin-comedy-love-1201306514/|dead-url = no}}</ref>此劇以「對約會交往實實在在的觀察」為主題，透過主角米琪（Mickey）和葛斯（Gus），用男女不同的角度來探索各種戀愛關係。<ref>{{Cite web|last = Carlson|first = Jay|date = 31 July 2015|url = http://indierevolver.com/2015/07/31/indie-revolver-exclusive-a-synopsis-and-very-early-look-at-the-judd-