== 劇情概要 ==
該影集以“腳踏實地看待的約會”的形式呈現，通過分別由雅各布斯和魯斯特扮演的角色米奇和格斯探索男性和女性對浪漫關係的看法。<ref>{{cite web|last=Carlson|first=Jay|date=31 July 2015|url=http://indierevolver.com/2015/07/31/indie-revolver-exclusive-a-synopsis-and-very-early-look-at-the-judd-apatow-created-netflix-original-series-love-starring-gillian-jacobs-and-paul-rust/|title=A Synopsis and Very Early Look at the Judd Apatow Created Netflix Original Series 'Love' Starring Gillian Jacobs and Paul Rust|publisher=IndieRevolver.com|access-date=23 September 2015|archive-date=6 May 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506011859/https://indierevolver.com/2015/07/31/indie-revolver-exclusive-a-synopsis-and-very-early-look-at-the-judd-apatow-created-netflix-original-series-love-starring-gillian-jacobs-and-paul-rust/|url-status=live}}</ref>米奇和格斯是兩個不值得信任的人，每個人都帶著沉重的情感包袱，試圖建立相互信任的關係；米奇是個[[酗酒|酗酒]]者、愛/性癮君子、攪局者，而且往往對自己和他人不誠實，而格斯則很笨拙、情感上需要幫助、對社交暗示視而不見，並且在事情不順時容易爆發走他的路。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/2018/03/love-series-finale-discussed.html|title='Love' Netflix Finale: What Happens to Mickey and Gus?|first=Jen|last=Chaney|date=16 March 2018|work=Vulture|access-date=11 August 2020|archive-date=3 August 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803090717/https://www.vulture.com/2018/03/love-series-finale-discussed.html|url-status=live}}</ref>

